00:16:19.210 --> 00:16:22.410 align:middle line:10%
So we go from a transcendent
non-physical state

00:16:22.410 --> 00:16:27.000 align:middle line:10%
of being-ness,
basically essence,

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:33.250 align:middle line:10%
to an imminent and present
state of existence physicality.

00:16:33.250 --> 00:16:36.940 align:middle line:10%
And then we go back to a
transcendent non-physical state

00:16:36.940 --> 00:16:37.740 align:middle line:10%
of being.

00:16:37.740 --> 00:16:40.460 align:middle line:10%


00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:45.790 align:middle line:10%
You are always in a state of
being and a state of beginning.

00:16:45.790 --> 00:16:48.118 align:middle line:10%
It doesn't change.

00:16:48.118 --> 00:16:50.410 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What do you think
of what he just said, Anita?

00:16:50.410 --> 00:16:52.220 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: Oh,
it rings so true.

00:16:52.220 --> 00:16:53.020 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It does.

00:16:53.020 --> 00:16:54.760 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: It does, totally.

00:16:54.760 --> 00:16:56.806 align:middle line:90%
And it's beautiful to see--

00:16:56.806 --> 00:17:02.260 align:middle line:84%
to see things like that
kind of endorse or that

00:17:02.260 --> 00:17:05.890 align:middle line:84%
say what I'm trying to say,
and he puts it very elegantly.

00:17:05.890 --> 00:17:10.029 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Now today, what would
you say about your cancer?

00:17:10.029 --> 00:17:10.829 align:middle line:90%
Gone?

00:17:10.829 --> 00:17:12.520 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Gone.

00:17:12.520 --> 00:17:13.720 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: 100%?

00:17:13.720 --> 00:17:14.520 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Yes.

00:17:14.520 --> 00:17:16.240 align:middle line:84%
Because five weeks
after I came out

00:17:16.240 --> 00:17:18.550 align:middle line:84%
of the near-death
experience, the doctors

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:21.970 align:middle line:84%
tried to do every test
possible because they

00:17:21.970 --> 00:17:23.589 align:middle line:90%
couldn't believe it was gone.

00:17:23.589 --> 00:17:25.030 align:middle line:90%
They could find no trace of it.

00:17:25.030 --> 00:17:28.270 align:middle line:84%
They even said, cancer
doesn't disappear like that.

00:17:28.270 --> 00:17:30.550 align:middle line:84%
We got to keep looking
till we find it.

00:17:30.550 --> 00:17:34.600 align:middle line:84%
But five weeks after the
NDE, they sent me home

00:17:34.600 --> 00:17:36.460 align:middle line:90%
to live my life cancer-free.

00:17:36.460 --> 00:17:41.320 align:middle line:84%
That was in March of
2006 and today it's 2019.

00:17:41.320 --> 00:17:43.030 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What did they say?

00:17:43.030 --> 00:17:45.700 align:middle line:84%
What did they think
when they realized

00:17:45.700 --> 00:17:47.980 align:middle line:84%
that you've gone
from a stage four

00:17:47.980 --> 00:17:51.050 align:middle line:90%
to zero in a matter of weeks?

00:17:51.050 --> 00:17:53.530 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: So there was
a lot of mixed reactions.

00:17:53.530 --> 00:17:57.010 align:middle line:84%
Most of them were really
shocked and blown away

00:17:57.010 --> 00:17:59.270 align:middle line:84%
and didn't know
what to make of it.

00:17:59.270 --> 00:18:01.070 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Were they
arguing with each other?

00:18:01.070 --> 00:18:01.987 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: They were.

00:18:01.987 --> 00:18:04.120 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You gave us the
wrong report or something?

00:18:04.120 --> 00:18:05.890 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: They
were wondering even

00:18:05.890 --> 00:18:07.600 align:middle line:90%
like when they first staged it.

00:18:07.600 --> 00:18:10.060 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is, even
the staging of it,

00:18:10.060 --> 00:18:11.200 align:middle line:90%
it was a progression.

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:13.870 align:middle line:84%
I had had so many
tests in the four

00:18:13.870 --> 00:18:16.670 align:middle line:90%
years since being diagnosed.

00:18:16.670 --> 00:18:18.310 align:middle line:84%
So they couldn't
argue with that.

00:18:18.310 --> 00:18:20.470 align:middle line:84%
There were different
doctors that had treated me.

00:18:20.470 --> 00:18:22.220 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And they all
said the same thing.

00:18:22.220 --> 00:18:24.380 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: And they'd
all said the same thing.

00:18:24.380 --> 00:18:26.770 align:middle line:84%
And one of the
doctors, my oncologist

00:18:26.770 --> 00:18:31.030 align:middle line:84%
at that time, I shared
with him that I had the NDE

00:18:31.030 --> 00:18:32.950 align:middle line:90%
and he completely believed me.

00:18:32.950 --> 00:18:34.600 align:middle line:90%
He said, you're not the only--

00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:37.630 align:middle line:84%
you're not the first person I've
heard something like this from.

00:18:37.630 --> 00:18:40.030 align:middle line:90%
What was interesting was that--

00:18:40.030 --> 00:18:43.210 align:middle line:84%
then, because people
started talking about me

00:18:43.210 --> 00:18:45.870 align:middle line:84%
and I became a little
bit of talk of the--

00:18:45.870 --> 00:18:47.440 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: A little
myth and legend?

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:48.240 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Yes.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:50.320 align:middle line:84%
A bit of a legend in
the city where I lived.

00:18:50.320 --> 00:18:53.770 align:middle line:84%
And so then newspaper came
and did an interview on me,

00:18:53.770 --> 00:18:55.750 align:middle line:90%
a journalist interviewed me.

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:59.260 align:middle line:84%
And then she said to me,
would your oncologist

00:18:59.260 --> 00:19:01.310 align:middle line:84%
back you up if I
interviewed your oncologist?

00:19:01.310 --> 00:19:02.410 align:middle line:90%
And I said, sure, he will.

00:19:02.410 --> 00:19:03.593 align:middle line:90%
He completely believed me.

00:19:03.593 --> 00:19:04.510 align:middle line:90%
He knew what happened.

00:19:04.510 --> 00:19:04.940 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Of course.

00:19:04.940 --> 00:19:07.360 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: But when she
interviewed my oncologist,

00:19:07.360 --> 00:19:09.770 align:middle line:90%
he didn't completely back me up.

00:19:09.770 --> 00:19:10.570 align:middle line:90%
He sort of--

00:19:10.570 --> 00:19:11.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He was afraid
of public ridicule.

00:19:11.890 --> 00:19:13.990 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: He was afraid
of public ridicule.

00:19:13.990 --> 00:19:15.820 align:middle line:84%
Since then, people
have said to me

00:19:15.820 --> 00:19:18.400 align:middle line:84%
that if he was
seen as a quack, he

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:20.998 align:middle line:84%
would have had his license,
his medical license, revoked.

00:19:20.998 --> 00:19:22.540 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What was
his excuse, though?

00:19:22.540 --> 00:19:23.410 align:middle line:90%
What did he say?

00:19:23.410 --> 00:19:24.660 align:middle line:90%
He had to admit it was gone.

00:19:24.660 --> 00:19:26.327 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: Oh, he
admitted it was gone.

00:19:26.327 --> 00:19:29.410 align:middle line:84%
He admitted it was a
spontaneous remission

00:19:29.410 --> 00:19:31.540 align:middle line:84%
and that I was
lucky to be alive.

00:19:31.540 --> 00:19:35.650 align:middle line:84%
But the-- everything
I attributed it to,

00:19:35.650 --> 00:19:37.600 align:middle line:90%
he said it was my mind.

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:41.330 align:middle line:84%
He didn't think that I had
experienced what I experienced.

00:19:41.330 --> 00:19:44.380 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He's saying that
there's a medical reason why

00:19:44.380 --> 00:19:45.920 align:middle line:90%
your body fought this off.

00:19:45.920 --> 00:19:46.720 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Yes.

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:48.520 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It doesn't
happen in every case.

00:19:48.520 --> 00:19:48.800 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Yes.

00:19:48.800 --> 00:19:49.842 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: But it happened.

00:19:49.842 --> 00:19:52.660 align:middle line:84%
And the fact that you had
a near-death experience,

00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:54.860 align:middle line:84%
and it's something mystical
that helped heal you--

00:19:54.860 --> 00:19:55.660 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: Yes.

00:19:55.660 --> 00:19:56.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: He wasn't
going to go there.

00:19:56.890 --> 00:19:58.557 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: He wasn't
going to go there.

00:19:58.557 --> 00:20:01.840 align:middle line:84%
Even though he could not
explain how it disappeared.

00:20:01.840 --> 00:20:05.140 align:middle line:84%
Other oncologists who were
not related to my case,

00:20:05.140 --> 00:20:07.540 align:middle line:84%
who later studied
my medical records,

00:20:07.540 --> 00:20:10.030 align:middle line:84%
said that whichever
way they look at it,

00:20:10.030 --> 00:20:11.410 align:middle line:90%
I shouldn't be alive.

00:20:11.410 --> 00:20:14.590 align:middle line:84%
Because there was no way
those billions of cancer cells

00:20:14.590 --> 00:20:16.198 align:middle line:84%
could have left my
body so quickly.

00:20:16.198 --> 00:20:17.740 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you have
any idea how you

00:20:17.740 --> 00:20:19.450 align:middle line:90%
got this in the first place?

00:20:19.450 --> 00:20:21.170 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: How
I got the cancer?

00:20:21.170 --> 00:20:22.270 align:middle line:90%
Yes, I do.

00:20:22.270 --> 00:20:26.320 align:middle line:10%
I feel that-- so it goes
a little bit to a lot

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:28.240 align:middle line:10%
of the things that
I learned while,

00:20:28.240 --> 00:20:32.440 align:middle line:10%
or what I realized in that
state of being in the NDE,

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:35.020 align:middle line:10%
I realized that actually--

00:20:35.020 --> 00:20:38.280 align:middle line:10%
I think all of us, but
certainly a lot of us,

00:20:38.280 --> 00:20:42.160 align:middle line:10%
we're actually not just five
sensory physical beings.

00:20:42.160 --> 00:20:43.690 align:middle line:90%
We are more than that.

00:20:43.690 --> 00:20:47.430 align:middle line:84%
We are-- I'll call it
six sensory beings,

00:20:47.430 --> 00:20:49.180 align:middle line:84%
for want of a better
term, because there's

00:20:49.180 --> 00:20:51.320 align:middle line:90%
no language to describe this.

00:20:51.320 --> 00:20:54.790 align:middle line:84%
But we know our soul
comes here with a calling

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:57.100 align:middle line:84%
and we know there's
something more to life

00:20:57.100 --> 00:21:00.070 align:middle line:84%
than just this physical
life, this world we live in,

00:21:00.070 --> 00:21:02.740 align:middle line:84%
this competitiveness
dog-eat-dog world.

00:21:02.740 --> 00:21:05.810 align:middle line:84%
Actually, internally, our soul
knows there's something more.

00:21:05.810 --> 00:21:06.610 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Sure does.

00:21:06.610 --> 00:21:09.490 align:middle line:90%
>>MOORJANI: But we suppress it.

00:21:09.490 --> 00:21:12.160 align:middle line:84%
Because we're afraid
that if we explore it,

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:15.620 align:middle line:84%
we're termed as being crazy
or woo-woo or whatever.

00:21:15.620 --> 00:21:18.430 align:middle line:84%
Now, I always knew there
was something more,

00:21:18.430 --> 00:21:20.290 align:middle line:90%
but I always suppressed it.

00:21:20.290 --> 00:21:24.460 align:middle line:84%
What I realized was that
because I had always

00:21:24.460 --> 00:21:28.750 align:middle line:84%
suppressed who I
am, I had literally

00:21:28.750 --> 00:21:30.010 align:middle line:90%
suppressed my own soul.

00:21:30.010 --> 00:21:31.900 align:middle line:90%
But with me, it was--

00:21:31.900 --> 00:21:33.550 align:middle line:84%
I mean, not everybody
gets cancer.

00:21:33.550 --> 00:21:36.070 align:middle line:84%
But with me, there was a
lot more going on than that.

00:21:36.070 --> 00:21:39.230 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot of
it was because--

00:21:39.230 --> 00:21:42.020 align:middle line:84%
in my case, to do with,
maybe, my culture,

00:21:42.020 --> 00:21:43.880 align:middle line:90%
with being an Indian woman.

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:45.860 align:middle line:84%
There was a lot of
gender disparity.

00:21:45.860 --> 00:21:48.800 align:middle line:90%
I had always made myself small.

00:21:48.800 --> 00:21:51.230 align:middle line:90%
I had always dimmed my light.

00:21:51.230 --> 00:21:56.900 align:middle line:84%
And I was-- in the culture
I grew up in, a woman's--

00:21:56.900 --> 00:22:01.490 align:middle line:84%
a woman's worth, her value,
is dependent on how valuable

00:22:01.490 --> 00:22:04.850 align:middle line:84%
she is to the men in her
community, in her life.

00:22:04.850 --> 00:22:07.110 align:middle line:84%
So the smaller
you make yourself,

00:22:07.110 --> 00:22:08.840 align:middle line:90%
the more you are rewarded.

00:22:08.840 --> 00:22:13.670 align:middle line:84%
And so I had always wanted
to do and be something more.

00:22:13.670 --> 00:22:16.650 align:middle line:84%
I'd always wanted to be
independent, but I could--

00:22:16.650 --> 00:22:19.490 align:middle line:90%
I'd always had to squash myself.

00:22:19.490 --> 00:22:24.350 align:middle line:84%
And so it was a lifetime
of suppressing myself,

00:22:24.350 --> 00:22:27.090 align:middle line:84%
and being a people
pleaser, and a doormat.

00:22:27.090 --> 00:22:29.120 align:middle line:84%
And it was only when I
was on the other side

00:22:29.120 --> 00:22:31.880 align:middle line:84%
that I realized I wasn't
supposed to do that.

00:22:31.880 --> 00:22:33.920 align:middle line:90%
That I have a lot to share.

00:22:33.920 --> 00:22:35.958 align:middle line:84%
That I'm supposed to
shine my light brightly.

00:22:35.958 --> 00:22:38.000 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You've got a
great story to tell people.

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:40.660 align:middle line:84%
What do you think
caused the remission?

00:22:40.660 --> 00:22:42.830 align:middle line:90%
Now that you look back.

00:22:42.830 --> 00:22:47.330 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: The realization
that actually we are, all of us,

00:22:47.330 --> 00:22:50.030 align:middle line:84%
are more powerful than
we realize, including me.

00:22:50.030 --> 00:22:53.390 align:middle line:84%
I had made myself so
small and insignificant

00:22:53.390 --> 00:22:58.040 align:middle line:84%
to the point of being invisible
that my body was crying out

00:22:58.040 --> 00:23:00.440 align:middle line:84%
and that's why it
manifested disease.

00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:03.920 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't listen to it so
it kept manifesting disease.

00:23:03.920 --> 00:23:08.300 align:middle line:84%
But all of us are stronger and
more powerful than we believe.

00:23:08.300 --> 00:23:12.650 align:middle line:84%
Our bodies are capable
of more than we have

00:23:12.650 --> 00:23:14.270 align:middle line:90%
been conditioned to believe.

00:23:14.270 --> 00:23:17.930 align:middle line:84%
It's almost like-- it feels to
me, this is just my opinion--

00:23:17.930 --> 00:23:20.990 align:middle line:84%
it feels like we've
been dumbed down.

00:23:20.990 --> 00:23:26.600 align:middle line:84%
And I know doctors are great
and the doctors I've dealt with

00:23:26.600 --> 00:23:30.740 align:middle line:84%
were wonderful people, but I
think that our medical paradigm

00:23:30.740 --> 00:23:34.370 align:middle line:84%
has dumbed down what our bodies
are actually capable of doing

00:23:34.370 --> 00:23:37.520 align:middle line:84%
and doesn't take into
consideration that we're not

00:23:37.520 --> 00:23:39.140 align:middle line:90%
just--

00:23:39.140 --> 00:23:41.990 align:middle line:84%
we're not just three
dimensional physical bodies.

00:23:41.990 --> 00:23:43.940 align:middle line:90%
We are a lot more than that.

00:23:43.940 --> 00:23:48.500 align:middle line:84%
And what determines
our health is actually

00:23:48.500 --> 00:23:53.450 align:middle line:84%
more than just your
medical condition.

00:23:53.450 --> 00:23:55.700 align:middle line:90%
It's your soul, your calling.

00:23:55.700 --> 00:23:57.890 align:middle line:90%
It's your reason for living.

00:23:57.890 --> 00:24:02.660 align:middle line:84%
The more passion you have for
life, the healthier you are.

00:24:02.660 --> 00:24:05.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What do you think
your doctors are saying

00:24:05.300 --> 00:24:08.510 align:middle line:84%
behind closed doors now,
or at a dinner table

00:24:08.510 --> 00:24:09.908 align:middle line:90%
with friends, about you?

00:24:09.908 --> 00:24:11.450 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: Oh, they
know it happened

00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:13.140 align:middle line:90%
and they're questioning things.

00:24:13.140 --> 00:24:15.770 align:middle line:84%
I had one of the doctors
who was treating me,

00:24:15.770 --> 00:24:18.770 align:middle line:84%
not the one that threw me
under the bus in the interview,

00:24:18.770 --> 00:24:22.140 align:middle line:84%
but another one who was
treating me all the way through.

00:24:22.140 --> 00:24:25.040 align:middle line:84%
He contacted me several
months ago and he said,

00:24:25.040 --> 00:24:29.180 align:middle line:84%
I just need to tell you that
ever since your experience,

00:24:29.180 --> 00:24:31.250 align:middle line:90%
I have never--

00:24:31.250 --> 00:24:34.140 align:middle line:84%
he said it is completely
changed the way that I

00:24:34.140 --> 00:24:34.940 align:middle line:90%
practice medicine.

00:24:34.940 --> 00:24:35.720 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Wow.

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:37.095 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: And
he said, however,

00:24:37.095 --> 00:24:40.760 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't ready to completely
embrace it at that time

00:24:40.760 --> 00:24:43.220 align:middle line:84%
because I would have
to throw out everything

00:24:43.220 --> 00:24:44.960 align:middle line:90%
I learned in medical school.

00:24:44.960 --> 00:24:49.130 align:middle line:84%
He said he actually went through
a traumatic time of his own

00:24:49.130 --> 00:24:52.670 align:middle line:90%
trying to reconcile everything.

00:24:52.670 --> 00:24:56.450 align:middle line:84%
Because once he saw my
experience, you know,

00:24:56.450 --> 00:24:58.700 align:middle line:84%
it kind of opened
his eyes or his mind,

00:24:58.700 --> 00:25:01.340 align:middle line:84%
he started seeing more
and more things like that.

00:25:01.340 --> 00:25:04.550 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Sadly, Anita,
not everybody gets healed.

00:25:04.550 --> 00:25:08.240 align:middle line:84%
Not everybody has a
success story that you had.

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:10.860 align:middle line:90%
Why you and not them?

00:25:10.860 --> 00:25:12.830 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: So the first
thing I want to say

00:25:12.830 --> 00:25:17.520 align:middle line:90%
is that death is not a failure.

00:25:17.520 --> 00:25:21.680 align:middle line:84%
People who pass on, if it's
their time, it's their time.

00:25:21.680 --> 00:25:25.340 align:middle line:84%
But also maybe at the
time, even if they

00:25:25.340 --> 00:25:27.260 align:middle line:84%
get a glimpse of
the other side, I

00:25:27.260 --> 00:25:29.570 align:middle line:84%
don't blame them for
wanting to stay there.

00:25:29.570 --> 00:25:32.150 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't mean they don't
love the people here enough

00:25:32.150 --> 00:25:34.850 align:middle line:84%
to not come back,
but it could mean

00:25:34.850 --> 00:25:37.220 align:middle line:84%
that they can complete
their purpose in a bigger

00:25:37.220 --> 00:25:41.620 align:middle line:84%
way from that state, that
state of transcendence,

00:25:41.620 --> 00:25:44.000 align:middle line:84%
because death is a
state of transcendence.

00:25:44.000 --> 00:25:47.360 align:middle line:84%
If people have lost a
loved one, maybe they're

00:25:47.360 --> 00:25:50.450 align:middle line:84%
the ones who are the lucky
ones, and me, who got sent back,

00:25:50.450 --> 00:25:51.690 align:middle line:90%
maybe I'm the unlucky one.

00:25:51.690 --> 00:25:52.490 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Maybe.

00:25:52.490 --> 00:25:54.650 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: And maybe they're
more transcended than I am.

00:25:54.650 --> 00:25:56.360 align:middle line:84%
Maybe they've completed
their work here.

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:57.860 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do we all
have this ability

00:25:57.860 --> 00:26:00.090 align:middle line:90%
to heal ourselves from within?

00:26:00.090 --> 00:26:01.160 align:middle line:90%
In your opinion?

00:26:01.160 --> 00:26:03.080 align:middle line:84%
>>MOORJANI: In my
opinion, I believe we do.

00:26:03.080 --> 00:26:06.290 align:middle line:84%
Unless it's our time
to pass, or unless we

00:26:06.290 --> 00:26:10.020 align:middle line:84%
want to go over there because we
feel we can do more from there.

00:26:10.020 --> 00:26:12.290 align:middle line:84%
But I think that if
we still have work

00:26:12.290 --> 00:26:14.090 align:middle line:90%
to do here, yes, absolutely.

00:26:14.090 --> 00:26:18.350 align:middle line:84%
I believe our bodies are
far, far more powerful

00:26:18.350 --> 00:26:20.592 align:middle line:84%
and has this really
strong ability

00:26:20.592 --> 00:26:22.550 align:middle line:84%
to heal more so than
we've been led to believe.

00:26:22.550 --> 00:26:24.360 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Dr. Joe
Dispenza of course,

00:26:24.360 --> 00:26:27.170 align:middle line:84%
is an expert on this
area of self-healing

00:26:27.170 --> 00:26:30.710 align:middle line:84%
and I had a chance to interview
him on "Beyond Belief."

00:26:30.710 --> 00:26:33.020 align:middle line:10%
>>JOE DISPENZER: Can
you teach your body

00:26:33.020 --> 00:26:36.080 align:middle line:10%
emotionally what that
future is going to feel

00:26:36.080 --> 00:26:37.770 align:middle line:10%
like before it's made manifest?

00:26:37.770 --> 00:26:40.020 align:middle line:10%
That means you can't
wait for your healing

00:26:40.020 --> 00:26:42.030 align:middle line:10%
to feel gratitude and wholeness.

00:26:42.030 --> 00:26:43.800 align:middle line:10%
You can't wait for
your wealth to feel

00:26:43.800 --> 00:26:45.000 align:middle line:10%
abundance and worthiness.

00:26:45.000 --> 00:26:47.670 align:middle line:10%
You can't-- you can't wait for
the mystical moment to feel

00:26:47.670 --> 00:26:48.470 align:middle line:10%
awe.

00:26:48.470 --> 00:26:50.940 align:middle line:10%
That's the old model of
reality of cause and effect.

00:26:50.940 --> 00:26:52.830 align:middle line:10%
That's Newtonian physics.

00:26:52.830 --> 00:26:55.350 align:middle line:10%
But the new model of reality,
the quantum model of reality,

00:26:55.350 --> 00:26:56.530 align:middle line:10%
is about causing an effect.

00:26:56.530 --> 00:26:59.072 align:middle line:10%
Which means the moment you start
feeling gratitude and whole,

00:26:59.072 --> 00:27:00.450 align:middle line:10%
your healing begins.

00:27:00.450 --> 00:27:02.940 align:middle line:10%
The moment you start
feeling worthy and abundant,

00:27:02.940 --> 00:27:04.380 align:middle line:10%
you're generating wealth.

00:27:04.380 --> 00:27:06.390 align:middle line:10%
The moment you're
in awe of life,

00:27:06.390 --> 00:27:08.730 align:middle line:10%
you're going to have
a mystical experience.

00:27:08.730 --> 00:27:12.060 align:middle line:10%
So then, your body is
your unconscious mind.

00:27:12.060 --> 00:27:15.570 align:middle line:10%
