between an actual experience

00:27:15.570 --> 00:27:18.240 align:middle line:10%
in your life that creates
an emotion and an emotion

00:27:18.240 --> 00:27:20.350 align:middle line:10%
that you can create
by thought alone.

00:27:20.350 --> 00:27:23.430 align:middle line:10%
So the body is believing it's
living in that future reality

00:27:23.430 --> 00:27:24.690 align:middle line:10%
in the present moment.

00:27:24.690 --> 00:27:26.190 align:middle line:10%
And what's the
significance of that?

00:27:26.190 --> 00:27:28.980 align:middle line:10%
As I said, the latest
research in genetics

00:27:28.980 --> 00:27:31.985 align:middle line:10%
says genes don't create disease.

00:27:31.985 --> 00:27:33.360 align:middle line:10%
It's the environment
that signals

00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:35.850 align:middle line:10%
the gene that creates change.

00:27:35.850 --> 00:27:38.520 align:middle line:10%
Well, if the end product of an
experience in the environment

00:27:38.520 --> 00:27:42.405 align:middle line:10%
is an emotion, the moment you
embrace an elevated emotion,

00:27:42.405 --> 00:27:44.530 align:middle line:10%
you're signaling the gene
ahead of the environment.

00:27:44.530 --> 00:27:45.840 align:middle line:10%
And what do genes do?

00:27:45.840 --> 00:27:46.980 align:middle line:10%
Genes make proteins.

00:27:46.980 --> 00:27:48.810 align:middle line:10%
And what are proteins
responsible for?

00:27:48.810 --> 00:27:50.970 align:middle line:10%
The structure and
function of your body.

00:27:50.970 --> 00:27:53.940 align:middle line:10%
And the expression of proteins
is the expression of life.

00:27:53.940 --> 00:27:56.700 align:middle line:10%
And if you keep knocking on
that genetic door over and over

00:27:56.700 --> 00:27:59.310 align:middle line:10%
again, you're going to
begin to up-regulate

00:27:59.310 --> 00:28:00.950 align:middle line:10%
the genes for health,
and you're going

00:28:00.950 --> 00:28:03.265 align:middle line:10%
to down-regulate the
genes for disease,

00:28:03.265 --> 00:28:05.640 align:middle line:10%
and all of a sudden you're
going to wake up in your dream

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:07.680 align:middle line:10%
and realize that you're
a different person.

00:28:07.680 --> 00:28:11.970 align:middle line:10%
And the personality now that had
the disease is no longer you.

